original: As the lamp's genie, I've witnessed remarkable moments unfold. A humble artist sketched her first masterpiece, immortalizing fleeting beauty; an orphan discovered a loving family, distant memories forgotten; a scientist's cure ended an age-old affliction, saving countless lives. Kings amassed riches or silenced foes, yet none derived true fulfillment. A generous heart gave away wealth, hearts touc
